	<h1 id="3D-Solvation-Structures-on-CaF$_2$">3D Solvation Structures on CaF$_2$<a class="anchor-link" href="#3D-Solvation-Structures-on-CaF$_2$">&#182;</a></h1><p>UHV measurements at 4K are all very well, but some applications require a more <em>fluid</em> environment</p>
	<ul>
	  <li>solar cells</li>
	  <li>batteries</li>
	  <li>photocathode / anodes</li>
	</ul>
