<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<h1 id="Conclusions">Conclusions<a class="anchor-link" href="#Conclusions">&#182;</a></h1><ul>
<li>Evidence suggests here that stable tips are not very invasive – measurement of equilibrium water density</li>
<li>Theory vs experiment: short range forces above Ca. </li>
<li>Better agreement between implicit tip model and experiment than explicit MD<ul>
<li>better tip models are needed!</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Towards mapping specific ion adsorption sites and exploring electrolyte solutions<ul>
<li>need to be cleverer than brute force to simulate</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
